tr.th: Conclusion and Recommendations based on this report and previous findings known to us

tr.td: All measured parameters are within normal limits except for a mildly elevated HbA1c (5.8%), indicating prediabetes. Renal function, electrolytes, and glucose are normal. Recommend lifestyle modification and follow-up HbA1c monitoring to assess glycemic control and prevent progression to diabetes.
